OL,3,CAnnual wealth tax proposed in Scottish
OL,4,CGreen election plans
OL,6,FThe Scottish Greens have proposed
OL,7,Fintroducing an annual tax which
OL,8,Ftargets the wealth of the "super rich".
OL,10,FLorna Slater, the party's co-leader,
OL,11,Fsaid the plans would raise #70 billion
OL,12,Fa year to fund public services like
OL,13,Fthe NHS.
OL,15,FThe policy is set to be part of the
OL,16,FScottish Green manifesto, which will
OL,17,Fbe published in the weeks ahead of the
OL,18,FGeneral Election, and will include
OL,19,Ftaxing the wealthiest 1% of UK
OL,20,Fhouseholds.
