OL,3,CAnnual wealth tax proposed in Scottish
OL,4,CGreen election plans
OL,6,FIt would start at a 1% tax rate for
OL,7,Fthose with assets worth #3.4 million,
OL,8,Frising to 5% for those with #5.7
OL,9,Fmillion and above.
OL,11,FA 10% rate would be imposed for those
OL,12,Fwith assets of at least #18.2 million.
OL,14,FIt comes after the party announced on
OL,15,FFriday it would put forward a record
OL,16,F44 candidates to contest seats at the
OL,17,Felection.
