OL,6,FMs Slater said: "The last few years
OL,7,Fhave been really tough for millions of
OL,8,Ffamilies across the UK. People have
OL,9,Fstruggled with sky high bills, soaring
OL,10,Fcosts and stagnating wages.
OL,12,F"Yet, for the super wealthy things
OL,13,Fhave never been better. They have
OL,14,Fcontinued to get richer while
OL,15,Finequality has got worse and worse.
