OL,3,CAnnual wealth tax proposed in Scottish
OL,4,CGreen election plans
OL,6,F"There is more than enough money in
OL,7,Fthe UK to ensure that everyone can
OL,8,Fgrow up with warmth and security, but
OL,9,Fso much of it is being hoarded by a
OL,10,Ftiny number of extremely wealthy
OL,11,Fpeople who don't need it.
OL,13,F"A fair income tax system is
OL,14,Fimportant, but it misses the vast
OL,15,Fmajority of the money being
OL,16,Faccumulated by the super rich. That is
OL,17,Fwhy it is so crucial that we tax their
OL,18,Foverall wealth.
